### 2. Database Layer

#### [NEW] [database.py](file:///c:/Users/LENOVO/Downloads/mr_ai_rag_v2/mr_ai_rag_v2/app/core/database.py)
- SQLAlchemy `create_engine` + `SessionLocal`
- `Base = declarative_base()`
