#### [NEW] [models.py](file:///c:/Users/LENOVO/Downloads/mr_ai_rag_v2/mr_ai_rag_v2/app/core/models.py)
Tables:
- [clients](file:///c:/Users/LENOVO/Downloads/mr_ai_rag_v2/mr_ai_rag_v2/app/core/clients.py#49-54) — id (PK), client_id, name, email, password_hash, token, is_verified, created_at, last_login
- [api_keys](file:///c:/Users/LENOVO/Downloads/mr_ai_rag_v2/mr_ai_rag_v2/app/routes/apikeys.py#139-155) — id, key_id, client_id (FK), name, key_hash, key_preview, is_active, created_at, request_count
- [chat_history](file:///c:/Users/LENOVO/Downloads/mr_ai_rag_v2/mr_ai_rag_v2/app/core/clients.py#161-165) — id, client_id (FK), role, content, sources (JSON), timestamp
- `notifications` — id, client_id (FK), type, message, is_read, created_at
- `email_otp` — id, email, otp_hash, expires_at, used

