- `generate_otp()` and `store_otp()` / `verify_otp()`

#### [MODIFY] [app/routes/clients.py](file:///c:/Users/LENOVO/Downloads/mr_ai_rag_v2/mr_ai_rag_v2/app/routes/clients.py)
