## Verification Plan

1. Install new deps: `pip install sqlalchemy psycopg2-binary`
2. Create PostgreSQL DB + run `CREATE TABLE` migrations via SQLAlchemy `Base.metadata.create_all()`
3. Register → get OTP email → enter OTP → create account → dashboard
4. Generate API key → appears in dashboard keys list + notification fires
5. Settings ⚙️ → Forgot Password flow → receive email OTP → reset
6. Home page logged-out state → upload disabled → login → upload works

---

## Database Setup Required

> [!CAUTION]
> You need a running PostgreSQL instance. Set `DATABASE_URL` in [.env](file:///c:/Users/LENOVO/Downloads/mr_ai_rag_v2/mr_ai_rag_v2/.env):
> ```
> DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:password@localhost:5432/mrairag
> ```
> Run `CREATE DATABASE mrairag;` in psql before starting the server. Tables are auto-created on startup.
